title: Chris Wallace dissects tough question of how China can be 'held accountable' for COVID-19 outbreak
description: "Fox News Sunday" anchor Chris Wallace said on "America's Newsroom" on Friday that he is "not sure how you hold China accountable" for the COVID-19 outbreak.
